high_descs: Turn right and walk into the next room to face the right end of the desk.
Pick up the disk on the left on the desk.
Take a step back to face the shelf on the right side of the desk.
Place the disk on the shelf on the right bottom of the desk.
Look up to face the disk on the top of the desk.
Pick up the disk on the top of the desk.
Look down to face the first disk on the shelf.
Place the disk next to the first disk on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: To move two disks on the desk to the shelf on the bottom right of the desk.

high_descs: Walk forward for two steps, turn right past the bed then turn left, walk four steps then turn right for six steps, turn right for four steps, turn left and walk to the desk.
Pick up the CD from the desk, on the upper left.
Turn around and walk one step, and then turn around and stop.
Put the CD in the open area below the desk top, at the lower, left front corner.
Turn to the right for one step, turn left for one step.
Pick up the CD from the top of the desk.
Turn all the way around and stop.
Place the CD to the right of the CD in the open area under the desk top.
anns.task_desc: Put two CDs in the open area between the desk top and the drawers underneath.

high_descs: Turn right and go around the book shelf to the right side of the desk.
Pick up the CD on the left of the gray bowl on the top of the desk
Move over left to the front of the drawer shelf under the desk top.
Place the CD on the shelf on the left side.
Move over right to the front of the other CD on the top of the desk.
Pick up the CD near the front edge of the desk.
Move over left to the front of the drawer shelf.
Place the CD on the right of the first CD on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Move two CDs on the desk to the drawer shelf.
